				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/C%E1%BA%A9m-th%E1%BB%A5-h%C3%A0nh/poem-U9ZNi9BzMmjWZ4V23lrQDA">Cẩm thụ hành - 錦樹行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/K%C3%ADnh-gi%E1%BA%A3n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-minh-ph%E1%BB%A7/poem-_e4g9bhzjOYKdlbtbHpUCQ">Kính giản Vương minh phủ - 敬簡王明府</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%A1n/K%C3%BD-t%E1%BA%B7ng-Nh%E1%BB%8B-Kh%C3%AA-ki%E1%BB%83m-ch%C3%ADnh-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%E1%BB%A8ng-Long/poem-RkVNbp6E0CezNjdXB8SkAA">Ký tặng Nhị Khê kiểm chính Nguyễn Ứng Long - 寄贈蕊溪檢正阮應龍</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%A1n/author-h_HbFCmxWKkwxboqzaEfNA">Trần Nguyên Đán</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-S%C3%B9ng-Ho%C3%A1n/Ng%E1%BB%A5c-trung-%C4%91%E1%BB%91i-nguy%E1%BB%87t/poem-YjlH0LItDtk3J4HpP-9Dsw">Ngục trung đối nguyệt - 獄中對月</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-S%C3%B9ng-Ho%C3%A1n/author-khnDeiNFO_ApZONPmFuNuA">Viên Sùng Hoán</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-ng%E1%BB%B1-tri%E1%BB%81u-b%C3%A1i-kh%C3%A1nh-l%C6%B0%E1%BB%A1ng-t%C3%B4n-cung-%E1%BB%A9ng-ch%E1%BA%BF/poem-GITjfN0kxcOSIJZsmXv1hQ">Phụng hoạ ngự triều bái khánh lưỡng tôn cung ứng chế - 奉和御朝拜慶兩尊宮應制</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-t%E1%BA%B7ng-Vi-t%E1%BA%A3-th%E1%BB%ABa-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BB%8B-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-LHzRT_2tYsZxedOAYTvWlg">Phụng tặng Vi tả thừa trượng nhị thập nhị vận - 奉贈韋左丞丈二十二韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/X%C3%A0-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/Quan-san-nguy%E1%BB%87t/poem-Id_LLv_c0AC4nAJxy71ckw">Quan san nguyệt - 闗山月</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/X%C3%A0-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/author-OTOkL6TRbM0V41YwHIzvfA">Xà Tường</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/Thu-h%C3%A0/poem-CS5xpQpEVbxs0O8zoJ86Xg">Thu hà - 秋霞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/author-GrfZ83486gEgzshT4ctASA">Đoàn Nguyễn Tuấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-ho%C3%A0ng-t%C3%A2y-tu%E1%BA%A7n-nam-kinh-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-05/poem-FLHtHYPcAQxN_7jqfa_RPg">Thượng hoàng tây tuần nam kinh ca kỳ 05 - 上皇西巡南京歌其五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-K%E1%BB%B3/T%E1%BB%91ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ph%E1%BB%A7/poem--k_4mpeEDk_Q04XEO8OhHA">Tống Trần Chương Phủ - 送陳章甫</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-K%E1%BB%B3/author-YrFgVDhYiheqwKg7ob0-Ig">Lý Kỳ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
